=Sun Bin 孫臏=
descendant of [[孫武]] and author of [[孫臏兵法]], a work that was lost already in the Han dynasty. 1972 the [[孫臏兵法]]  was excavated
from two Han graves near [[銀雀山]].
===Keywords===
[[孫武]] [[銀雀山]]
==Works==
* [[孫臏兵法]]
==Literature==
===PhD Dissertations===
* Edmund Balmforth: A Chinese Military Strategist of the Warring States: Sun Pin. Rutgers University, 1979
===Monographs===
* [[Ralph D. Sawyer]]: Sun Pin Military Methods. Boulder: Westview Press, 1995